---
description: Top user journeys—stable selectors, state waits, no flake tolerance
alwaysApply: false
---

# E2E tests

Cover main journeys (value/safety), not every screen. Selectors: `data-testid`, roles, text—not brittle CSS. Wait on UI/network state, not blind sleep. Clean auth/storage per test. Save screenshots/trace on fail. Flakes = bugs to fix—don’t paper over with retries.
